  "title": "Crumbly Vegetarian Herbal Crumble",
  "description": "A decadent and indulgent Venezuelan dish featuring a blend of herbs, yellow peppers, and other vegetables in a crumbly texture that's perfect for breakfast or as a side.",
  "cuisine": "Venezuelan",
